definitions.definition: ( sometimes capitalized ) The 15th letter of the Classical and Modern Greek alphabets ( 16th in Ancient and Old Greek ), used in ordering lists as in naming ( astronomy ) the 15th star of a constellation or ( epidemiology ) the 15th discovered major variant of a disease .

main_definition: ( sometimes capitalized ) The 15th letter of the Classical and Modern Greek alphabets ( 16th in Ancient and Old Greek ), used in ordering lists as in naming ( astronomy ) the 15th star of a constellation or ( epidemiology ) the 15th discovered major variant of a disease .
( virology , pathology ) Ellipsis of Omicron variant .
